news.message: Last Chance to Get Nyx and Rhino Prime!

translations.en: Last Chance to Get Nyx and Rhino Prime!
translations.fr: Dernière chance pour Nyx Prime et Rhino Prime!
translations.it: Ultima opportunità di ottenere Nyx e Rhino Prime!
translations.de: Letzte Chance, euch Nyx und Rhino Prime zu holen!
translations.es: ¡Última oportunidad para obtener a Nyx y Rhino Prime!
translations.pt: Última chance para obter a Nyx e o Rhino Prime!
translations.ru: Последний шанс получить Никс и Рино Прайм!
translations.pl: Ostatnia szansa, aby zakupić Nyx i Rhino Prime!
translations.tr: Nyx ve Rhino Prime'a sahip olmak için son şans!
translations.ja: NyxとRhinoのPrime Vault終了まであとわずか！
translations.zh: 获得 Rhino Prime 及 Nyx Prime 的最后机会！
translations.ko: 닉스와 라이노 프라임을 손에 넣을 마지막 기회!
translations.tc: 獲得 Nyx 和 Rhino Prime 的最後機會！
